original_font_information.description:
In 2014, the widely known Lemon/Milk was intentionally made as a visual identity for a zine with the same name published by students of English Study Program, University of Indonesia.

Continiously developed, in this pro version, Lemon/Milk finally has lowercases, as well as oldstyle figure, case sensitive form etc. It also covers Latin, Cyrillic, and Greek.

MARSNEV
